            <title><![CDATA[【[感冒]#如何区分呼吸道合胞病毒和流感#】呼吸道合胞病毒一般在冬春季比较多见，今年的感染高峰相对延迟，最近有不少孩子感染。呼吸道合胞病毒通过飞沫和密切接...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%86%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%92%8C%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#如何区分呼吸道合胞病毒和流感#</span></a>】呼吸道合胞病毒一般在冬春季比较多见，今年的感染高峰相对延迟，最近有不少孩子感染。呼吸道合胞病毒通过飞沫和密切接触传播，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A9%B4%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E5%BC%B1%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A9%B4%E5%B9%BC%E5%84%BF%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E5%BC%B1%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%98%93%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E9%81%93%E5%90%88%E8%83%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#婴幼儿和体弱老人易感染呼吸道合胞病毒#</span></a>，症状主要表现为鼻塞、流涕、咳嗽、喘息等。而流感病毒感染症状相对较重，以高热为主，往往出现浑身酸痛、恶心呕吐等症状👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4904844658409515" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1he96susngcj61oj0y2kjl02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/2VZ0uQiMlx085GmkFF0I01041200DjKt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684905473&amp;ssig=XjJyn%2ByQ9d&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9zjgSXDTlx085Gmk9iL601041200laho0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684905473&amp;ssig=l2zLsldK2z&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XhWgA91jlx085GmjMaRO01041200dESS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1684905473&amp;ssig=rBmdCbkzxh&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4904844658409515&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
